{
  "stem": "13584.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was warm around the stove when it was a fire there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But when it was not fire, it was cold, terribly cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My mother used to warm there water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know what for.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "OK, to the school, I did not go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then from there, my mother start to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know-- she was working for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We moved to a different place, in the same place, in the same city, I mean, the same-- Chiili.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We lived-- and apparently my mother picked up-- picked up a house-- apartment-- a room in the worst neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were thieves and robbers living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But-- but they didn't touch us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Usually thieves and robbers never touch anybody from their immediate neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother used to go to work, and I used to stay with my brother all day, locked up with a little hook inside this-- this room.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the same furniture we had in this room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a shelf along the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the shelf was nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] One day-- it was a summer day-- please, I was a child-- a summer day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, a plane-- a two-flat plane-- I don't know how you call in this-- old fashioned plane-- landed not far from the place we used to live.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the way, not far-- maybe-- maybe 300 yards, a quarter of a mile-- was already the-- the wilderness, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The wilderness started with sand, with dunes of sand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the plane landed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked through the little window, and I see all of the kids from the neighborhood are running to see the plane.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother said not to go out, but I wanted to see the plane.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
